baseline: Early diagnosis and treatment in this population are both complicated by symptoms of alcohol withdrawal and controversial because of the belief that alcoholics will abuse anxiolytics.
high_intensity: Early diagnosis and treatment in this population are both complicated by symptoms of alcohol withdrawal and controversial because of the belief that alcoholics will severely abuse anxiolytics.
low_intensity: Early diagnosis and treatment in this population are both complicated by symptoms of alcohol withdrawal and controversial because of the belief that alcoholics may misuse anxiolytics.

baseline: Few psychologists have engendered the controversy or endured the abuse that Arthur Jensen has in the past three decades.
high_intensity: Few psychologists have engendered the controversy or endured the relentless abuse that Arthur Jensen has in the past three decades.
low_intensity: Few psychologists have engendered the controversy or endured the criticism that Arthur Jensen has in the past three decades.

baseline: The abuse of volatile solvents, or inhalants, is an enduring problem among adolescents although a number of factors obscure the nature and extent of this drug using behavior.
high_intensity: The severe abuse of volatile solvents, or inhalants, is an enduring problem among adolescents although a number of factors obscure the nature and extent of this harmful drug using behavior.
low_intensity: The misuse of volatile solvents, or inhalants, is an ongoing issue among adolescents although a number of factors obscure the nature and extent of this drug using behavior.

baseline: Insider trading scandals on Wall Street have focused public attention on the abuse of money and power in the service of greed.
high_intensity: Insider trading scandals on Wall Street have intensely focused public attention on the rampant abuse of money and power in the service of greed.
low_intensity: Insider trading scandals on Wall Street have brought public attention to the misuse of money and power in the service of greed.

baseline: The differences between somatic psychiatrists and mental hygienists, already apparent earlier, became much more pronounced during the Depression years, partly as a consequence of their different perspectives on this social crisis.
high_intensity: The stark differences between somatic psychiatrists and mental hygienists, already apparent earlier, became much more pronounced during the severe Depression years, partly as a consequence of their opposing perspectives on this devastating social crisis.
low_intensity: The differences between somatic psychiatrists and mental hygienists, already apparent earlier, became somewhat more pronounced during the economic downturn years, partly as a consequence of their varied perspectives on this social issue.

baseline: Cognitive bibliotherapy is an effective treatment of subthreshold depression.
high_intensity: Cognitive bibliotherapy is an effective treatment for major depressive episodes.
low_intensity: Cognitive bibliotherapy is an effective treatment of mild depression.

baseline: A technique recently developed in the mental_health field is Goal Attainment Scaling (GAS).
high_intensity: A groundbreaking technique recently developed in the dynamic mental_health field is Goal Attainment Scaling (GAS).
low_intensity: A technique recently developed in the field is Goal Attainment Scaling (GAS).

baseline: Data obtained from the parents and teachers of children randomly selected from public Pre-K classrooms in 6 states (N = 415) and from a mental_health screening of rural and urban children (N = 5,577) support the validity and reliability of ABLE.
high_intensity: Data obtained from the parents and teachers of children randomly selected from public Pre-K classrooms in 6 states (N = 415) and from an urgent mental_health screening of rural and urban children (N = 5,577) emphatically support the strong validity and reliability of ABLE.
low_intensity: Data obtained from the parents and teachers of children randomly selected from public Pre-K classrooms in 6 states (N = 415) and from a general screening of rural and urban children (N = 5,577) support the validity and reliability of ABLE.

baseline: Some attribute DID to childhood trauma and others attribute it to iatrogenesis.
high_intensity: Some attribute DID to severe childhood trauma and others attribute it to iatrogenesis.
